You must not have made your self owner…

go to characters>your character’s name> and change his right under character rights to 3 for owner, 2 for admin, and mod cant do pickup, 1

item.title: [Help me!] Spawning in Moparscape [Help me!]
item.dc:creator: @jjones10 jjones10
item.description:
@jjones10 wrote:

The first four stars refers to a item id. i.e. 0995
The second four stars refers to the amount i.e. 999999

A succesful command to get 999999 gold is ::pickup 0995 999999

item.dc:creator: @Gamerstips Gamerstips
item.description:

Make sure you didnt use caps.

And, If you are doin a 3 digit pickup code, you need to add a zero before it

::pickup 0995 1000
